## Project Structure

```
src/
├── features/[feature]/
│   ├── components/           # Shared components
│   ├── [region]/             # Region-specific (ph, my, id)
│   │   ├── phone/            # Phone UI
│   │   └── tablet/           # Tablet UI
│   ├── hooks/                # Feature hooks
│   └── utils/                # Feature utilities
├── screens/[screen]/
│   ├── [screen].tsx          # Delegates to phone/tablet
│   ├── [screen].phone.tsx    # Phone implementation
│   └── [screen].tablet.tsx   # Tablet implementation
└── hooks/useBoundStore.tsx   # Zustand combined store
```

